_sText: README FIRST: This is a first public BETA version ! Its a remake or clone from surf_japan. But i did it COMPLETE NEW FROM THE SCRATCH! Not decompiled and edited like the other ones around here. I know the filesize is big (30 megabytes - without lightning 6 megabytes) and the FPS isnt real improved - but this a lack of the maindesign of the map. DESCRIPTON: The most of you should know about this map. Its not a real surfmap in my eyes, its more a funmap. There is a basic jail and a bombspot. The bomspot is closed until you press the "B" button somewhere ^^ so look around for it. There is also a buyzone in this beta. Its really not finished so please post your comments and ideas for the final one. For more screenshots and futher informations about this work goto: H-E-R-E ;-)
